20day-to-day%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Bill%20and%20Lydia%20needed%20additional%20income.%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20they'd%20both%20suffered%20from%20health%20issues%2C%20including%20Bill%20breaking%20his%20leg%2C%20which%20kept%20them%20from%20working.%20They%20relied%20solely%20on%20Social%20Security%2C%20Bill's%20small%20pension%20of%20%24335%20a%20month%20from%20his%20time%20at%20the%20local%20TV%20station%20in%20advertising%20sales%2C%20and%20some%20savings.%20But%20when%20they%20couldn't%20sustain%20their%20lifestyle%20anymore%20that%20year%2C%20Lydia%20drove%20down%20the%20road%20to%20the%20closest%20Home%20Depot%20and%20applied%20for%20a%20job.%20Home%20Depot%20hired%20her%20at%20%2416%20an%20hour%20in%20the%20electrical%20department.%20She%20was%2079.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lydia%20Hinds%20at%20Home%20Depot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6879175085e81483682e3274%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELydia%20works%20between%2017%20and%2024%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20though%20her%20hours%20some%20weeks%20have%20been%20cut.%3Cp%3EMichael%20J.%20Fiedler%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20loved%20it%20at%20first%2C%20and%20I%20still%20enjoy%20my%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Lydia%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20I%20started%20there%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20I%20had%20heart%20failure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Lydia%20noticed%20tasks%20like%20sewing%20curtains%20and%20gardening%20knocked%20her%20out%2C%20a%20doctor%20found%20that%20her%20heart%20was%20not%20pumping%20nearly%20enough%20blood.%20At%20work%20each%20day%2C%20she's%20expected%20to%20clean%20appliances%2C%20keep%20aisles%20tidy%2C%20and%20help%20customers%20with%20their%20needs%20for%20%2419.55%20an%20hour.%20Still%2C%20she%20kept%20her%20sense%20of%20humor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20got%20the%20echocardiogram%2C%2