%20and%20his%20work%20at%20the%20TV%20station.%20Lydia%20met%20Bill%20through%20a%20dating%20service%20in%201995.%20He%20picked%20her%20up%20for%20their%20first%20date%20in%20a%20white%20limousine%2C%20wearing%20a%20camel-hair%20coat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20going%20on%20dates%20with%20three%20women%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20when%20I%20saw%20her%2C%20I%20dropped%20them%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20had%20glasses%20three%20times%20bigger%20than%20he%20needed%2C%20which%20I%20took%20care%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20Lydia%20jokes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20marriage%2C%20theirs%20has%20had%20its%20ups%20and%20downs.%20After%20a%20brief%20stint%20in%20Florida%2C%20they%20returned%20to%20Connecticut%20and%20spent%20most%20of%20their%20savings%20on%20a%20house%20that%20required%20more%20repairs%20than%20they%20had%20expected.%20Lydia%20had%20moved%20on%20from%20the%20now-closed%20mail%20stores%20and%20was%20working%20as%20a%20real%20estate%20agent%2C%20but%20says%20she%20rarely%20made%20enough%20money%20to%20be%20comfortable.%20Bill%20had%20left%20the%20TV%20station%20in%201994%20to%20focus%20on%20his%20band%20and%20was%20playing%20at%20weddings%2C%20teaching%20piano%20lessons%2C%20and%20selling%20pianos.%20They%20had%20been%20able%20to%20save%20a%20little%20throughout%20their%20career%2C%20but%20never%20enough%20to%20think%20they%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-early-with-enough-money-for-one-year-no-regrets-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretire%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20put%20almost%20all%20of%20our%20money%20into%20that%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Lydia%20says.%20She%20says%20they%20bought%20it%20for%20%24185%2C000%20in%202002%20and%20spent%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000%20on%20renovations.%20%26quot%3BIt%20looked%20a%20lot%20better%2C%20and%20we%20figured%20we'd%20flip%20it%20and%20do%20OK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%202008%20recession%20hit%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20ton%20of%20bricks%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20they%20had%20%2475%2C000%20invested%20in%20the%20market%2C%20but%20as%20the%20market%20fell%2C%20they%20pulled%20from%20their%20account%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20increased%20mortgage%20and%20property%20taxes.%20The%20couple%20hoped%20they'd%20get%20some%20money%20out%20of%20the%20home%20they'd%20renovated.%20But%20they%20defaulted%20on%20their%20mortgage%20in%202015%2C%20and%20a%20forced%20sale%20brought%20only%20%24115%2C000.%20They%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy.%20The%20income%20from%20a%20side%20business%20Lydia%20had%20started%20to%20help%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-retirees-sell-stuff-downsize-retirement-housing-senior-move-manager-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edownsize%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20the%20piano%20lessons%20that%20Bill%20gave%2C%20weren't%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FUeErF%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FUeErF%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20among%20the%20more%20than%2010%20million%20Americans%20who%20lost%20their%20homes%20due%20to%20the%20Great%20Recession.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20took%20over%20five%20years%20to%20fully%20bounce%20back%20after%20dropping%20more%20than%20half%20its%20value%20from%20its%20high%20in%202007%20to%20its%20lowest%20point%20in%202009.%20For%20thousands%20of%20households%20approaching%20retirement%20age%2C%20this%20meant%20working%20longer%20after%20their%20savings%20shriveled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility.%20We've%20made%20mistakes%2C%20but%20also%2C%20who%20knew%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22h