0who%20had%20all%20those%20hopes%20dashed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20a%20good%20number%20of%20older%20adults%20are%20susceptible%20to%20a%20major%20life%20event%20that%20can%20knock%20out%20a%20major%20chunk%20of%20their%20savings%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsda.berkeley.edu%2Fsdaweb%2Fanalysis%2F%3Fdataset%3Dscfcomb2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESurvey%20of%20Consumer%20Finances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bottom%20fifth%20of%20households%20headed%20by%20someone%2075%20and%20older%20had%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20about%20%2475%2C000%20in%202022%2C%20including%20equity%20built%20up%20in%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20Hindses%20are%20bracing%20for%20another%20life-shattering%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20lose%20her%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20says.%20%26quot%3BShe%20feels%20the%20same%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f22a6774-f9d7-45fb-a315-bfd598ff6948%5C%22%3EWorking%20to%20survive%20and%20holding%20on%20to%20each%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20days%20after%20work%2C%20Lydia%20sits%20at%20her%20computer%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-retire-no-jobs-older-americans-work-money-struggles-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eapplies%20for%20any%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20could%20reasonably%20do.%20She%20tries%20to%20appear%20as%20sprightly%20as%20possible%20in%20her%20applications%2C%20sometimes%20emphasizing%20how%20she%20graduated%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Hartford%20mid-career%20in%201994.%20Though%20she%20omits%20her%20age%20from%20her%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20she%20suspects%20that%20employers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20tell%2C%20preventing%20her%20from%20landing%20anything%20higher-paying%20than%20Home%20Depot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20counter%20her%20many%20rejections%2C%20she%20started%20bui