nderburg%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20anti-ageism%20nonprofit%20Changing%20the%20Narrative.%20%26quot%3BMany%20of%20the%20job%20boards%20for%20older%20workers%20are%20focused%20on%20lower-paid%20jobs%20where%20there's%20a%20demand.%20If%20you%20cannot%20pay%20your%20mortgage%2C%20your%20rent%2C%20whatever%20it%20is%2C%20and%20you%20need%20to%20work%2C%20it's%20better%20to%20do%20something%20than%20nothing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20programs%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dol.gov%2Fagencies%2Feta%2Fseniors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESenior%20Community%20Service%20Employment%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%20help%20lower-income%20Americans%2055%20and%20older%20get%20job%20training%2C%20the%20two%20dozen%20aging%20and%20work%20researchers%20and%20organization%20executives%20BI%20spoke%20to%20agreed%20there%20should%20be%20more%20resources%20for%20older%20Americans%20in%20the%20workplace.%20This%20could%20include%20more%20conversations%20with%20workplace%20leadership%20about%20advocating%20for%20older%20workers%2C%20more%20training%20on%20technology%20topics%20like%20AI%2C%20or%20local%20legislation%20codifying%20more%20protections%20against%20ageism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELydia%20and%20Bill%20hope%20to%20move%20out%20of%20their%20apartment%20before%20their%20rent%20rises%20again.%20It's%20increased%20by%20nearly%20%24300%20a%20month%20since%20they%20moved%20in%202019%2C%20but%20they%20have%20nowhere%20to%20go.%20They're%20waiting%20for%20an%20open%20cottage%20at%20a%20nearby%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-xers-burdened-long-term-care-costs-for-boomers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecare%20facility%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20cost%20%241%2C650%20for%20a%20one-bedroom%20unit%2C%20but%20they've%20rethought%20whether%20that%20would%20be%20feasible%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20be%20in%20a%20place%20where%20if%20something%20happens%2C%20we're%20still%20together%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20we%20can%20visit%20each%20other%20easily%2C%26quot%3B%20Lydia%20says.%20With%20all%20the%20financial%20strain%2C%20some%20days%2C%20Lydia%20wants%20to%20give%20up%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20hell%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lydia%20and%20Bill%20Hinds%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687919773d5881a51c1d843c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBill%20can%20no%20longer%20work%2C%20but%20he%20spends%20as%20much%20time%20as%20he%20can%20with%20Lydia.%3Cp%3EMichael%20J.%20Fiedler%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20attributes%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-longevity-doctor-takes-these-3-supplements-daily-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elongevity%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20connection.%20They%20say%20they%20rarely%20fight%2C%20and%20when%20they%20do%2C%20it%20ends%20with%20laughs%20and%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20soulmates%2C%26quot%3B%20Lydia%20remarks%2C%20pointing%20to%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20relationship%20is%20vital%20because%20many%20people%20in%20their%20community%2C%20she%20says%2C%20are%20not%20well%20enough%20to%20live%20active%20lives.%20Plus%2C%20Lydia%20no%20longer%20speaks%20to%20her%20daughter%20after%20years%20of%20a%20souring%20relationship.%20Bill's%20relationship%20with%20his%20children%20is%20tighter.%20For%20his%2090th%20birthday%2C%20most%20of%20his%20family%20flew%20to%20Connecticut.%20They're%20about%20to%20become%20great-grandparents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20maintain%20friends%20on%20a%20budget%2C%20Bill%20says.%20They've%20set%20aside%20some%20money%20to%20visit%20a%20friend%20on%20Cape%20Cod%20in%20October%2C%20and%20Bill%20has%20plans%20to%20see%20a%20film%20with%20a%20friend.%20One%20of%20the%20downsides%20of%20aging%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20losing%20friends%20left%20and%20right.%20Many%20have%20died%2C%20while%20others%20have%20drifted%20away.%20Their%20Christmas%20dinner%20table%20of%2010%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20has%20dwindled%20to%20just%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20financial%20frustrations%20and%20loneliness%2C%20they%20find%20moments%20of%20solace.%20Now%20and%20then%2C%20they%20drive%20the%20half%20hour%20to%20Hartford%20in%20their%202023%20Hyundai%20Elantra%20for%20a%20concert%20or%20to%20the%20shore%20with%20their%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20often%2C%20it's%20the%20little%20moments%20that%20distract%20them%20from%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-purchases-financial-risks-economic-uncertainty-real-estate-careers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efinancial%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20five%20years%2C%20Bill%20sits%20at%20the%20piano%20in%20their%20community's%20clubhouse.%20He%20strikes%20a%20few%20chords%2C%20cringing%20as%20the%20notes%20sound%20slightly%20too%20dissonant%20for%20his%20liking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20perfect%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20Bill%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20shout%2C%20he%20can%20tell%20me%20what%20note%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Lydia%20whips%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20memory%2C%20he%20plays%20selections%20from%20Claude%20Debussy's%20%26quot%3BClair%20de%20Lune%26quot%3B%20and%20Fr%C3%A9d%C3%A9ric%20Chopin's%20%26quot%3BNocturnes%2C%26quot%3B%20missing%20a%20note%20here%20and%20there%20to%20his%20frustration.%20Tears%20stream%20down%20Lydia's%20face%20as%20he%20serenades%20her%20with%20the%20out-of-tune%20piano.%20When%20he%20finishes%20a%20prelude%2C%20she%20hugs%20him%20tightly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lydia%20embracing%20Bill%20Hinds%20at%20the%20piano%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68791994f748d8c055f5cca4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBill's%20mind%20is