80%9CI%20came%20across%20a%20Swedish%20athlete%20who%20cycled%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Nepal%2C%20climbed%20Everest%2C%20and%20then%20cycled%20back.%20That%20image%20just%20stayed%20with%20me.%20I%20thought%20if%20he%20can%20do%20it%2C%20why%20not%20someone%20from%20India%3F%20Why%20not%20someone%20from%20Tripura%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20question%20slowly%20transformed%20into%20a%20mission.%20Not%20only%20would%20he%20climb%20Everest%2C%20but%20he%E2%80%99d%20also%20cycle%20to%20Nepal%20and%20finish%20off%20with%20the%20Tenzing-Hillary%20Everest%20Marathon%20held%20every%20year%20on%20May%2029%2C%20commemorating%20the%20first%20successful%20summit%20by%20Sir%20Edmund%20Hillary%20and%20Tenzing%20Norgay%20in%201953.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20the%20whole%20journey%20to%20be%20land-based%20and%20low-carbon.%20Adventure%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20leave%20a%20large%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aritra%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20wheels%20for%2021%20days%2C%20covering%201%2C200%20km%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2016%20March%202024%2C%20Aritra%20took%20his%20first%20pedal%20stroke%20from%20Agartala%2C%20setting%20out%20for%20Nepal%20on%20a%20cycle%20loaded%20with%20basic%20supplies.%20The%20ride%20took%2021%20days%2C%20of%20which%2014%20were%20active%20cycling%20days%2C%20covering%20approximately%201%2C200%20kilometres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cycled%20around%2080%20to%20100%20kilometres%20a%20day%20and%20took%20rest%20days%20in%20between.%20I%20always%20started%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20never%20cycled%20after%20sundown.%20Safety%20was%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753498249.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aritra%20c