mes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdogs-punched-slammed-pet-groomer-assaulted-pets-during-sessions-arrested-after-viral-video-sparks-outrage%2Famp_articleshow%2F122912973.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20a%20'garbage%20rally'%20powered%20by%20junk%20stocks%20could%20explain%20quant%20hedge%20funds'%20no%20good%2C%20very%20bad%20summer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20contemplative%20and%20sad%20man%20sits%20at%20his%20laptop%20with%20a%20red%20hue.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64271a9645ef1b001984c0c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20contemplative%20and%20sad%20man%20sits%20at%20his%20laptop%20with%20a%20red%20hue.%3Cp%3ECrystal%20Cox%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EQuant%20hedge%20funds%20have%20been%20losing%20money%20since%20the%20start%20of%20June.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20causes%20are%20unclear%2C%20though%20execs%2C%20traders%2C%20and%20banks%20have%20pointed%20to%20a%20few%20factors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWednesday%20was%20another%20rough%20day%2C%20as%20the%20average%20quant%20lost%200.8%25%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20fundamental%20investing%20world%20marvels%20at%20another%20potential%20bubble%20made%20up%20of%20meme%20stocks%20and%20retail%20traders%2C%20quant%20hedge%20funds%20are%20trying%20to%20solve%20a%20much%20more%20complex%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20smartest%20people%20at%20the%20smart%20money%20firms%20have%20been%20on%20a%20weekslong%20losing%20streak%20starting%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20June%2C%20with%20firms%20like%20Qube%2C%20Two%20Sigma%2C%20and%20Point72's%20Cubist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquant-hedge-funds-losses-summer-cubist-qube-man-group-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuffering%20losses%20over%20that%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Wednesday%20was%20another%20rough%20day%20of%20trading%20for%20many%20funds%20as%20the%20average%20quant%20lost%200.8%25%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20prime%20brokerage%20unit%20said%20July%20was%20on%20track%20to%20be%20the%20worst%20month%20in%20five%20years%20and%20pointed%20to%20similar%20factors%20as%20it%20did%20earlier%20in%20the%20week%3A%20A%20momentum%20sell-off%2C%20crowded%20trades%2C%20and%20high%20volatility%20in%20certain%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20quant%20firms%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20steady-drip%20losses%20that%20have%20eroded%20a%20hot%20start%20to%20the%20year%20in%20systematic%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20isn't%20the%20only%20firm%20that's%20begun%20to%20wrap%20its%20head%20around%20what's%20happening.%20Computer-run%20managers%20have%20come%20up%20with%20theses%2C%20found%20parallels%20to%20past%20markets%2C%20and%20are%20even%20planning%20for%20a%20quick%20rebound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20belief%20taking%20hold%20is%20that%20broader%20market%20calamity%20is%20unlikely%20to%20spread%2C%20as%20the%20sources%20of%20pain%20aren't%20fundamental%20market%20weakness%20or%20a%20lurking%20economic%20maelstrom%2C%20but%20rather%20the%20opposite%3A%20a%20surprisingly%20strong%20economy%20that%20has%20flooded%20the%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20and%20questionable%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20with%20liquidity%20that%20happened%20to%20catch%20quants%20wrong-footed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDark%20Forest%20Technologies%20founder%20Jacob%20Kline%20wrote%20in%20a%20Friday%20note%20to%20investors%20that%20the%20current%20scenario%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20at%20all%20like%202007%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20forced%20deleveraging%20inflicted%20rapid%20losses%20across%20the%20systematic%20space.%20Kline%2C%20who%20was%20previously%20on%20the%20investment%20committee%20at%20Bridgewater%2C%20said%20this%20summer's%20swoon%20is%20a%20byproduct%20of%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20we%20politely%20call%20a%20'garbage%20rally.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20theorizes%20that%20the%20resurgence%20in%20heavily%20shorted%20junk%20stocks%20in%20recent%20weeks%20has%20forced%20some%20smaller%20quant%20firms%20to%20sell%20their%20positions%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20pain%20for%20everyone%20still%20holding%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bad%20month%20but%20not%20a%20crisis%3B%20the%20drivers%20are%20atypical%20but%20not%20surprising%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222c73e13c-b8d7-467e-a202-f108b4960847%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20Sydney%20Sweeney%20and%20the%20memestock%20crowd%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20give%20too%20much%20credit%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsydney-sweeney-meme-stock-american-eagle-jeans-wall-street-bets-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESydney%20Sweeney%20and%20the%20memestock%20crowd%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20were%20late%20to%20the%20ball%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20executive%20at%20a%20multimanager%20fund%20involved%20in%20quant%20strategies%20said%20some%20large%20funds%20started%20noticing%20losses%20before%20June.%20Weeks%20before%20Kohl's%20and%20American%20Eagle%20became%20retail%20darlings%2C%20some%20micro-cap%20stocks%20and%20thinly%20traded%20Chinese%20names%20%26quot%3Bhad%20been%20running%20for%20three%20weeks%20doing%20silly%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20underlying%20malady.%20No%20COVID.%20No%20great%20financial%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20multimanager%20exec%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20ascribes%20blame%20largely%20to%20a%20broader%20surge%20in%20market%20liquidity%20and%20risk%20appetite%2C%20a%20result%20of%20positive%20macroeconomic%20developments%20that%20began%20burbling%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Bpeculiar%20set%20of%20circumstances%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epreceded%20the%20quant%20bleeding%2C%20according%20to%20Kline.%20The%20broader%20stock%20market%20rally%20heading%20into%20June%20was%20largely%20driven%20by%20retail%20and%20systematic%20trend-following.%20Hedge%20funds%20had%20relatively%20low%20net%20exposure%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20had%20been%20hedging%20the%20quality%20stocks%20by%20shorting%20weak%20ones%2C%20which%20was%20profitable.%20The%20market%20reached%20all-time%20highs%20in%20June%2C%20and%20with%20prices%20so%20rich%2C%20hedge%20funds%20stopped%20adding%20to%20those%20high-quality%20stocks%20but%20also%20stopped%20betting%20against%20the%20weak%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemoving%20their%20short%20positions%20boosted%20%26quot%3Bgarbage%26quot%3B%20stocks%2C%20which%20attracted%20the%20attention%20of%20retail%20traders%20and%20meme%20stock%20enthusiasts%2C%20driving%20those%20positions%20up%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20quants%2C%20in%20simplistic%20terms%2C%20use%20their%20mathematical%20firepower%20to%20%26quot%3Bsort%20good%20from%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Kline%20put%20it%2C%20this%20rally%20in%20low-quality%20companies%20set%20many%20of%20them%20up%20for%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuants%20are%20generally%20going%20to%20be%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20that%20kind%20of%20arbitrary%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20Kline%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrategies%20that%20jump%20on%20short-term%20trends%20%26quot%3Bmay%20be%20exacerbating%26quot%3B%20the%20surge%2C%20said%20Antoine%20Haddad%2C%20founder%20of%20%241%20billion%20Bainbridge%20Partners%2C%20a%20multistrategy%20hedge%20fund%20with%20quant%20portfolio%20managers.%20This%20includes%20%26quot%3BAI-driven%20algos%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big-picture%20driver%20of%20this%20frenzied%20trading%20is%20the%20strong%20macroeconomic%20backdrop%20%E2%80%94%20low%20inflation%2C%20muted%20tariff%20impact%2C%20lack%20of%20rate%20hikes%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20attracted%20more%20money%20into%20the%20market.%20During%20Covid%20and%20the%20original%20memestock%20craze%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20market%20was%20awash%20in%20liquidity%2C%20and%20money%20gravitated%20to%20odd%20places%2C%20including%20seemingly%20worthless%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%20mention%20NFTs%2C%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20and%20SPACs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20happening%20in%202025%20is%20an%20echo%2C%20similar%20but%20far%20less%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20wrinkle%20and%20outgrowth%20of%20the%20increasing%20liquidity%20and%20risk%20appetite%20is%20the%20thaw%20in%20equity%20capital%20markets%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bhave%20lit%20up%20like%20a%20Christmas%20tree%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20multimanager%20exec%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20capital%20raising%20was%20dead%20much%20of%20this%20year%2C%20companies%20in%20June%20began%20raising%20money%20again%20through%20initial%20public%20offerings%2C%20follow-on%20raises%2C%20and%20convertible%20bonds%2C%20all%20of%20which%20%26quot%3Baccelerated%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20quarter%2C%20as%20global%20issuers%20and%20investors%20gained%20confidence%20amid%20a%20market%20rebound%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20mid-July%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20allows%20companies%2C%20%26quot%3Bgarbage%26quot%3B%20or%20otherwise%2C%20to%20improve%20their%20prospects%20by%20injecting%20their%20coffers%20at%20attractive%20valuations%2C%20potentially%20boosting%20their%20stock%20price%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20hedge%20funds%20closely%20monitor%20such%20activity%2C%20it's%20not%20traditionally%20the%20bailiwick%20of%20quants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuants%20don't%20sit%20in%20that%20business%20and%20they%20don't%20see%20that%20flow%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20multimanager%20exec%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287a2ef24-6577-4d42-ba98-20427e7d5851%5C%22%3EAll%20eyes%20on%20the%20industry's%20largest%20quant%20funds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20the%20source%20of%20the%20quant%20carnage%20is%20one%20question.%20Identifying%20when%20the%20pain%20will%20abate%20is%20equally%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20trader%20who%20works%20at%20one%20of%20the%20industry's%20largest%20quant%20funds%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20biggest%20firms%20will%20be%20the%20most%20significant%20factor%20over%20the%20next%20week.%20If%20these%20funds%20are%20forced%20to%20sell%2C%20then%20there%20could%20be%20serious%20pain%20that%20could%20impact%20everyone%20from%20Fidelity%20mutual%20funds%20to%20Robinhood%20retail%20traders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSome%20small%20players%20don't%20have%20a%20choice%20but%20to%20capitulate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20multimanager%20exec%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20larger%20firms%20know%20that%20if%20a%20major%20peer%20cuts%20its%20exposure%2C%20%26quot%3Bthen%20it%20becomes%20a%20bigger%20contagion%20and%20gets%20out%20of%20hand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20hasn't%20happened%20yet%2C%20and%20some%20are%20betting%20that%20the%20bigger%20players%20will%20just%20sit%20tight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20size%20of%20the%20funds%2C%20the%20pain%20tolerance%20of%20their%20executives%2C%20and%20the%20trust%20they%20have%20in%20their%20models%20is%20where%20the%20quant%20heavyweights%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20shine.%20They%20either%20have%20investor%20capital%20locked%20up%20for%20years%20or%20a%20giant%20horde%20of%20internal%20money%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20they%20can%20withstand%20losses%20for%20longer%2C%20especially%20if%20they%20anticipate%20a%20bounceback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDark%20Forest%20compared%20the%20situation%20to%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20when%20some%20smaller%20quants%20were%20stung%20by%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20signalling%20that%20lower%20rates%20may%20be%20coming.%20This%20increase%20of%20liquidity%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20caused%20a%20similar%20surge%20in%20stocks%20that%20quants%20were%20either%20short%20or%20not%20invested%20in.%20Those%20who%20%26quot%3Bpulled%20back%20missed%20out%20badly%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20funds%20that%20held%20firm%20saw%20substantial%20gains%20in%20the%20following%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%202023%2C%20the%20losses%20are%20big%20enough%20to%20where%20they%20are%20inducing%20the%20weaker%20hands%20to%20delever%2C%20which%20is%20exacerbating%20the%20losses%20this%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20reads.%20But%20this%20time%20around%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20hands%26quot%3B%20will%20let%20their%20models%20continue%20because%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ARKKs%20of%20the%20world%20are%20unlikely%20to%20keep%20outperforming%20the%20market%20by%2010%25%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Kline%20said%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ereferring%20to%20the%20innovation-focused%20ETF%20managed%20by%20Ark%20Investment%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20strong%20hands%20should%20be%20levering%20up%20into%20this%20headwind%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20executive%20of%20a%20small%20quant%20fund%20said%20they%20planned%20to%20ride%20out%20the%20%26quot%3Bfroth%20in%20sexy%20sectors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20going%20to%20suddenly%20switch%20our%20models%20over%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20had%20been%20a%20great%20year%20before%20the%20summer.%20Those%20conditions%20can%20come%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20multimanager%20exec%20believes%20the%20worst%20is%20over.%20It%20can%20take%20time%20for%20markets%20to%20recalibrate%20the%20junk%20stocks%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bnow%20that%20everyone%20is%20writing%20about%20it%2C%20we're%20probably%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquant-hedge-funds-losing-money-theories-cubist-qube-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753478301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6537ff7c96f7540cd064335d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquant-hedge-funds-losing-money-theories-cubist-qube-2025-7%22%2C%22summ