ple%20was%20a%2065-inch%20S90F%2C%20so%20my%20impressions%20also%20apply%20to%20the%2055-%20and%2077-inch%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20sizes%20have%20an%20incredibly%20thin%20frame%20that%20looks%20sleek%20and%20stylish.%20The%20S90F's%20profile%20is%20notably%20slimmer%20than%20many%20competing%20Mini%20LED%20TV%20models%2C%20like%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ftcl-qm8k-qled-4k-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETCL%20QM8K%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20since%20its%20OLED%20panel%20doesn't%20require%C2%A0space%20for%20a%20separate%20backlight.%20Its%20thickest%20point%20is%20only%201.6%20inches%2C%20where%20its%20back%20panel%20protrudes%20to%20house%20the%20TV's%20electronics%20and%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20Samsung%20S90F%20TV's%20rear%20and%20side%20ports.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883c0b785e81483682eb46a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20four%20HDMI%20ports%20support%20the%202.1%20standard%20for%20up%20to%204K%2F144Hz%20signals.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20display's%20ports%20are%20either%20side-%20or%20down-facing%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20TV%20to%20be%20mounted%20very%20close%20to%20the%20wall%20if%20desired.%20Despite%20requiring%20no%20screws%20to%20assemble%2C%20the%20included%20pedestal%20stand%20feels%20stable%20and%20holds%20the%20S90F%20well.%20It%20measures%2014.4%20inches%20wide%20by%2010.4%20inches%20deep%2C%20so%20it%20still%20comfortably%20fits%20on%20a%20thinner%20credenza%20or%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20four%20HDMI%20inputs%2C%20and%20they're%20all%20version%202.1%20with%20support%20for%20up%20to%20a%204K%2F144Hz%20signal.%20But%20to%20get%20full%20bandwidth%20capabilities%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20Input%20Signal%20Plus%20is%20activated%20in%20the%20TV's%20menu.%20The%20setting%20can%20be%20found%20by%20navigating%20to%20General%20%26amp%3B%20Privacy%2C%20then%20External%20Device%20Manager%2C%20then%20Input%20Signal%20Plus.%20You%20can%20turn%20this%20on%20for%20each%20HDMI%20input%2C%20and%20it%20enables%20the%20port%20to%20receive%20high-bandwidth%20signals.%20If%20it's%20set%20to%20off%2C%20the%20TV%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20display%20at%204K%2F120Hz%20(or%20144Hz%20for%20PC%20gaming).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20a%20hand%20holding%20a%20Samsung%20S90F%20remote%20in%20front%20of%20the%20TV%2C%20which%20is%20out%20of%20focus%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883c14ff748d8c055f64e92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20included%20SolarCell%20remote%20charges%20from%20sunlight%20and%20indoor%20lights.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S90F%20comes%20with%20Samsung's%20compact%20SolarCell%20remote%20with%20Alexa%20and%20Bixby%20voice%20control.%20There's%20an%20additional%20AI%20button%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20remote%20this%20year%2C%20but%20otherwise%2C%20its%20face%20is%20identical%20to%20previous%20models.%20The%20small%20size%20of%20the%20remote%20keeps%20all%20of%20its%20functions%20easily%20within%20thumb's%20reach%2C%20but%20the%20tiny%20buttons%20could%20be%20mildly%20frustrating%20to%20use%20if%20you're%20someone%20with%20large%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20remote's%20rear%20has%20a%20solar%20panel%20for%20charging%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20need%20batteries%2C%20and%20it%20has%20a%20USB-C%20port%20as%20a%20backup%20if%20you%20ever%20run%20out%20of%20juice%20from%20light%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242b4c1ed-9ff2-469c-8a19-51086c2b9f90%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20S90F's%20excellent%20color%20volume%20delivers%20vibrant%20images%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221925%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20Samsung%20S90F%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20town%20by%20a%20river.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883bf6885e81483682eb42b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S90F%20produces%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20colors%20thanks%20to%20its%20quantum%20dot%20technology.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20mentioned%20above%2C%20I%20reviewed%20the%2065-inch%20S90F%2C%20which%20uses%20a%20QD-OLED%20panel.%20One%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20a%20QD-OLED%20screen%20over%20regular%20OLED%20(called%20WOLED)%20is%20color%20volume.%20WOLEDs%20rely%20on%20white%20light%20that%20passes%20through%20a%20color%20filter.%20But%20QD-OLEDs%20use%20blue%20light%20with%20red%20and%20green%20quantum%20dots.%20Without%20getting%20too%20into%20the%20weeds%20with%20technical%20details%2C%20this%20process%20enables%20a%20QD-OLED%20to%20produce%20higher%20color%20volume%20with%20brighter%2C%20purer%20saturation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20my%20X-rite%20i1%20Pro%203%20spectrophotometer%2C%20C6%20HDR5000%20colorimeter%2C%20Murideo%20Seven-G%208K%20pattern%20generator%2C%20and%20Calman%20calibration%20software%20from%20Portrait%20Displays%2C%20I%20measured%20the%20S90F's%20P3%20color%20gamut%20coverage%20at%2099.78%25%20in%20Filmmaker%20Mode%20(the%20TV's%20most%20accurate%20setting).%20That's%20an%20exceptional%20number%20at%20the%20top%20end%20of%20what%20TVs%20can%20achieve.%20The%20P3%20color%20gamut%20is%20what%20modern%20high%20dynamic%20range%20(HDR)%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20use%2C%20so%20the%20S90F%20is%20capable%20of%20displaying%20the%20full%20range%20of%20colors%20that%20Hollywood%20productions%20are%20graded%20for.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20its%20color%20accuracy%20is%20excellent.%20This%20all%20results%20in%20bright%2C%20realistic%20colors%20that%20look%20stunning%20on%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20watched%20several%20HDR%20videos%20to%20test%20the%20TV's%20real-world%20performance.%20The%20explosions%20in%20%26quot%3BMad%20Max%3A%20Fury%20Road%26quot%3B%20burst%20in%20swirls%20of%20red%2C%20orange%2C%20and%20yellow.%20Skin%20tones%20looked%20natural%20and%20not%20overblown.%20The%20TV's%20accurate%2C%20vibrant%20hues%20accentuated%20the%20film's%20changing%20color%20palette%2C%20starkly%20delineating%20the%20red%20and%20yellow%20day%20sequences%20from%20the%20rich%20blue%20scenes%20at%20night.%20The%20S90F%20allowed%20the%20film's%20stylistic%20look%20to%20shine%20through%20and%20create%20a%20highly%20engaging%20cinematic%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221891%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20Samsung%20S90F%20OLED%20TV%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20lizard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883bfd085e81483682eb440%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221419%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV%20gets%20bright%20for%20a%20midrange%20OLED%20and%20offers%20sharp%20detail.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20like%20all%20Samsung%20TVs%2C%20the%20S90F%20doesn't%20support%20Dolby%20Vision%20HDR%2C%20instead%20opting%20for%20HDR10%2B%2C%20a%20competing%20royalty-free%20HDR%20format%20originally%20developed%20by%2020th%20Century%20Studios%2C%20Panasonic%2C%20and%20(surprise)%20Samsung.%20Both%20Dolby%20Vision%20and%20HDR10%2B%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20adjust%20the%20picture%20on%20a%20scene-by-scene%20or%20frame-by-frame%20basis%20to%20offer%20the%20most%20accurate%20HDR%20image%20your%20TV%20is%20capable%20of.%20But%20Dolby%20Vision%20content%20is%20more%20widespread%2C%20and%20it%20allows%20more%20fine-tuning%20in%20post-production%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20better%20performance.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20different%20high%20dynamic%20range%20formats%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHDR%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20benefits%20of%20Dolby%20Vision%20are%20too%20subtle%20to%20be%20considered%20a%20must-have%2C%20but%20this%20is%20one%20area%20where%20the%20S90F%20is%20a%20step%20behind%20OLEDs%20from%20LG%20and%20Sony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20brightness%2C%20though%2C%20the%20S90F%20edges%20out%20other%20OLEDs%20in%20this%20price%20range%20while%20also%20delivering%20a%20decent%20upgrade%20over%20last%20year's%20S90D.%20The%20S90D%20offered%20around%201%2C240%20nits%20of%20brightness%20on%20a%20standard%2010%25%20window.%20The%20S90F%20improves%20that%20number%20by%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20nits%2C%20with%20a%20max%20of%20around%201%2C457%20nits%20on%20a%2010%25%20window.%20Smaller%20window%20sizes%20can%20hit%20an%20even%20higher%20peak%20of%20around%201%2C620%20nits.%20This%20allows%20specular%20highlights%20(like%20explosions%20and%20light%20sources%20in%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows)%20to%20really%20pop.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20scene%20with%20stars%20against%20a%20black%20night%20sky%20sparkles%20with%20a%20wonderful%20intensity%20on%20the%20S90F.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S90F's%20OLED%20panel%20also%20enables%20perfect%20black%20levels%20when%20watching%20TV%20in%20a%20dark%20room%2C%20completely%20free%20from%20any%20of%20the%20patchiness%20or%20uneven%20backlighting%20that%20can%20pop%20up%20on%20QLED%20and%20Mini%20LED%20sets.%20That%20said%2C%20ambient%20light%20causes%20those%20black%20levels%20to%20slightly%20elevate%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20look%20a%20little%20gray%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20the%20TV's%20QD-OLED%20panel%20lacking%20a%20polarizing%20layer%2C%20which%20is%20something%20that%20LG's%20WOLEDs%20have.%20A%20TV's%20overall%20brightness%20is%20higher%20without%20this%20filter%2C%20but%20it%20also%20allows%20light%20to%20reflect%20internally%20and%20adversely%20affect%20the%20screen's%20black%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20regular%20viewing%2C%20this%20rise%20in%20black%20level%20is%20only%20slightly%20apparent%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20as%20distracting%20as%20it%20is%20on%20TVs%20that%20use%20a%20matte%20screen%20coating%2C%20like%20the%20flagship%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-s95f-oled-4k-tv-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESamsung%20S95F%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20in%20a%20room%20with%20ambient%20light%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20able%20to%20sit%20back%20and%20enjoy%20TV%20shows%20without%20any%20major%20issues.%20And%20though%20it%20does%20have%20a%20glossy%20finish%2C%20the%20S90F%20handles%20direct%20reflections%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221835%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20Samsung%20S90F%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20tractor%20in%20a%20field.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883c05f3d5881a51c1e0663%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20S90F's%20image%20quality%20remains%20excellent%20even%20when%20you%20view%20the%20screen%20from%20an%20angle.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Higgins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S90F%20also%20has%20extremely%20wide%20viewing%20angles%2C%20which%20is%20a%20benefit%20found%20on%20all%20OLED%20displays.%20There's%20no%20visual%20degradation%20to%20the%20color%20or%20brightness%2C%20even%20from%20more%20than%2060%20degrees%20off-axis.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20large%20group%20over%20to%20watch%20TV%20or%20a%20movie%2C%20you%20can%20be%20sure%20everyone%20is%20getting%20a%20similar%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20whole%2C%20the%20S90F's%20picture%20performance%20is%20remarkable%20for%20its%20price.%20Comp