llywood-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epodcasts%20often%20now%20start%20with%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20where%20the%20podcast%20role%20would%20sit%20inside%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20second%20person%20who%20had%20conversations%20with%20the%20company%20said%20they%20believed%20it%20would%20sit%20in%20Netflix's%20TV%20and%20film%20licensing%20arm%20under%20Lori%20Conkling%20rather%20than%20the%20original%20content%20side.%20That%20could%20signal%20that%20Netflix%20might%20look%20to%20license%20existing%20shows%2C%20as%20it's%20done%20with%20some%20YouTube%20creators%20like%20preschool%20entertainer%20Ms.%20Rachel%2C%20as%20well%20as%20make%20original%20shows%20with%20hosts.%20Separate%20content-side%20hires%20could%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdison%20Research%20has%20charted%20the%20continued%20rise%20of%20podcast%20listening.%20In%20a%20new%20report%20out%20this%20week%2C%20the%20firm%20said%2073%25%20of%20people%20ages%2012%20and%20over%20in%20the%20US%20listen%20to%20or%20watch%20podcasts%2C%20up%20from%2055%25%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20is%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20too%2C%20with%2051%25%20of%20people%2012%20and%20up%20saying%20they've%20watched%20a%20podcast%2C%20according%20to%20Edison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPodcast%20advertising%20grew%2026.4%25%20to%20%242.4%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iab.com%2Fnews%2Fdigital-ad-revenue-2024%2F%3Futm_source%3Dpodnews.net%26utm_medium%3Dweb%26utm_campaign%3Dpodnews.net%253A2025-04-21%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIAB%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emarketer.com%2Fcontent%2Fpodcast-ad-revenues-will-grow-consistently-despite-broader-ad-pullbacks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEMARKETER%3C%2Fa%3E%20projects%20it%20will%20top%20%242.5%20billion%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20media%20heavyweights%20have%20made%20big%20moves%20to%20chase%20the%20podcast-listening%20audience%20