20company%20expects%20total%20headcount%20to%20remain%20roughly%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20Microsoft%2C%20some%20staff%20speculated%20about%20what%20may%20have%20driven%20Nadella%20to%20write%20the%20memo%3A%20Are%20more%20job%20cuts%20coming%3F%20Is%20he%20feeling%20guilty%20about%20earnings%2C%20which%20the%20company%20is%20due%20to%20report%20next%20week%3F%20Was%20this%20just%20a%20message%20to%20Wall%20Street%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275e8031b-fbfa-49da-b268-bd219b717bec%5C%22%3ENadella%20knows%20employees%20are%20stressed%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENadella%20wrote%20the%20letter%20because%20he%20knows%20employees%20are%20stressed%20about%20increased%20performance%20pressure%2C%20AI%20competition%2C%20and%20job%20cuts%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%20Microsoft's%20last%20big%20employee%20%26quot%3BSignals%26quot%3B%20survey%20came%20out%20before%20the%20recent%20job%20cuts%2C%20but%20the%20company%20still%20gauges%20employee%20sentiment%20through%20daily%20and%20weekly%20%26quot%3Bpulse%26quot%3B%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20about%20220%2C000%20employees%2C%20so%20it's%20hard%20to%20externally%20gauge%20the%20sentiment%20across%20the%20workforce%20broadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20a%20company%20our%20size%2C%20you%20can%20imagine%20we%20have%20a%20variety%20of%20reactions%20internally%20that%20range%20from%20positive%20to%20constructive%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20spokesman%20Frank%20Shaw%20said.%20%26quot%3BSatya%20heard%20directly%20back%20from%20a%20number%20of%20employees%20who%20appreciated%20his%20leadership%20as%20well%20as%20the%20content%20and%20tone%20of%20his%20message.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d2f468e-0826-400d-a756-347a5ee9cf57%5C%22%3ECriticism%20from%20some%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReactions%20from%20some%20employees%2C%20shared%20directly%20with%20Business%20Insider%20and%20on%20an%20employee%20message%20board%2C%20provide%20a%20partial%20window%20into%20ho