ctus%20so%20she%20could%20spare%20her%20own%20planet%20from%20being%20destroyed%20by%20him.%20Earth%20is%20saved%2C%20but%20Sue%20looks%20to%20be%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichards%20tries%20to%20revive%20her%20but%20is%20unsuccessful.%20Franklin%20is%20crying%20and%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20his%20mother.%20Richards%20lays%20Franklin%20on%20her%20chest.%20Suddenly%2C%20Franklin%20revives%20Sue%20by%20putting%20his%20hands%20on%20her.%20Sue's%20eyes%20glow%2C%20and%20then%20she%20begins%20to%20breathe.%20She%20later%20tells%20Richards%20that%20their%20child%20is%20much%20more%20powerful%20than%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f358bb5e-b037-411a-a5d7-92921edb100a%5C%22%3EThe%20movie's%20mid-credits%20scene%20reveals%20how%20The%20Fantastic%20Four%20could%20be%20involved%20in%20'Avengers%3A%20Doomsday'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222622%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robert%20Downey%20Jr.%20in%20a%20green%20suit%20holding%20a%20silver%20mask%20and%20a%20microphone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883b31ef748d8c055f64bf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221967%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERobert%20Downey%20Jr.%20appeared%20onstage%20at%20Marvel's%20San%20Diego%20Comic-Con%20panel%20on%20July%2027%2C%202024%2C%20to%20reveal%20he%20is%20playing%20Doctor%20Doom.%3Cp%3EJesse%20Grant%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%20for%20Disney%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20clear%20that%20Franklin%20will%20be%20a%20major%20focus%20in%20future%20%26quot%3BFantastic%20Four%26quot%3B%20movies%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcu-movies-and-tv-series-ranked-by-critics-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20MCU%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20movie's%20mid-credits%20scene%20jumps%20to%20four%20years%20later%2C%20when%20Franklin%20is%20now%20a%20toddler%20and%20Sue%20is%20reading%20him%20a%20book.%20She%20walks%20away%20from%20him%20to%20get%20another%20b