e.%20He%20played%20because%20it%20was%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20made%20him%20feel%20alive%20and%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20brought%20him%20closer%20to%20his%20dream%20of%20studying%20at%20the%20Berklee%20College%20of%20Music%20in%20the%20United%20States%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20fingers%20moved%20across%20the%20strings%20and%20his%20voice%20wove%20through%20the%20street%20noise%2C%20people%20slowed%20down.%20Some%20paused.%20One%20filmed.%20The%20video%20travelled%20far%2C%20and%20with%20it%2C%20the%20name%20of%2015-year-old%20Debraj%20Bhattacharya.%20But%20behind%20the%20calm%20exterior%20of%20the%20now-viral%20busker%20lies%20a%20story%20shaped%20by%20personal%20loss%2C%20quiet%20grit%2C%20and%20the%20unwavering%20love%20between%20a%20father%20and%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHolding%20on%20to%20music%20after%20loss%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebraj%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20home%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391614%2Fparai-beat-history-caste-barriers-revival%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emusic%20was%20ever-present.%3C%2Fa%3E%20His%20mother%2C%20a%20singer%20herself%2C%20filled%20their%20small%20home%20with%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20until%20cancer%20took%20her%20away.%20Debraj%20was%20young%20when%20she%20passed%2C%20but%20the%20memory%20of%20her%20voice%20and%20love%20for%20music%20stayed%20on.%20It%20became%20a%20lifeline.%20A%20way%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20something%20that%20loss%20had%20almost%20taken%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-23T155712.602-1753266450.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Debraj%2C%20music%20became%20a%20lifeline%20after%20he%20lost%20his%20mother.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-23T155712.602-1753266450.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-23T155712.602-1753266450-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-23T155712.602-1753266450-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-23T155712.602-1753266450-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-23T155712.602-1753266450-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475004%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20Debraj%2C%20music%20became%20a%20lifeline%20after%20he%20lost%20his%20mother.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20father%2C%20Debashish%20Bhattacharya%2C%20once%20worked%20with%20a%20major%20production%20house%20but%20left%20it%20all%20to%20raise%20his%20son%20alone.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20transition%20was%20hard%2C%20but%20I%20made%20sure%20I%20stood%20by%20him%20and%20his%20dreams.%20We%20only%20have%20each%20other%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20enough%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20home%20was%20not%20just%20about%20survival.%20It%20was%20about%20nurturing%20a%20dream.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20may%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20for%20a%20middle-class%20person%20to%20do%20such%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20Debashish%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20I%20believe%20anything%20is%20possible%20if%20one%20has%20belief%2C%20grit%2C%20and%20passion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20lockdown%20in%202020%20that%20Debraj%20first%20picked%20up%20the%20guitar.%20With%20no%20formal%20background%20in%20music%20production%2C%20he%20began%20learning%20the%20instrument