0with%20a%20borrowed%20amp%20and%20his%20well-worn%20guitar%2C%20Debraj%20began%20busking%20on%20Park%20Street%20%E2%80%94%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20corridor%2C%20where%20old%20jazz%20clubs%20once%20hummed%20with%20life%20and%20Christmas%20lights%20still%20dazzle%20in%20December.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20expect.%20Would%20anyone%20stop%3F%20Would%20they%20care%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20one%20performance%2C%20earnest%2C%20hopeful%2C%20and%20unpolished%20most%20beautifully%2C%20struck%20a%20chord%20far%20beyond%20the%20city.%20The%20video%20spread%20quickly.%20But%20unlike%20most%20viral%20stories%2C%20this%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20about%20spectacle.%20It%20was%20about%20sincerity.%20About%20a%20teenager%20who%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20performing%2C%20but%20speaking%20from%20somewhere%20deeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20clip%20reached%20thousands%20and%20began%20a%20wave%20of%20support%20and%20recognition.%20%E2%80%9CI%20try%20to%20follow%20people%20like%20Sourav%20Ganguly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20balanced%20their%20careers%20and%20studies.%20I%E2%80%99m%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebraj%20is%20now%20a%20student%20who%20juggles%20academics%20and%20his%20music%20practice%2C%20aspiring%20to%20create%20compositions%20in%20both%20Eastern%20and%20Western%20classical%20genres.%20He%20has%20a%20deep%20admiration%20for%20artists%20like%20Ustad%20Amjad%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20Ustad%20Rashid%20Khan%2C%20Papon%20and%20Shankar%20Mahadevan.%20He%20also%20dreams%20of%20building%20fusion%20tracks%20that%20bring%20together%20the%20traditional%20with%20the%20modern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recently%20received%20an%20invitation%20to%20perform%20at%20the%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Science%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20marking%20one%20of%20his%20first%20big%20steps%20into%20the%20wider%20world%20of%20live%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20special%20moment%20at%20Deshaj%20Cafe%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20heartwarming%20invitations%20Debraj%20received%20came%20from%20Deshaj%20Caf%C3%A9%2C%20a%20venture%20of%20Moram%20Earth%20%E2%80%94%20a%20community-driven%20initiative%20based%20near%20Santiniketan%20that%20works%20with%20tribal%20artisans%20and%20emerging%20artists.%20Debraj%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20perform%20alongside%20singer%20Lagnajita%20Chakraborty%20during%20Deshaj%E2%80%99s%20eighth%20anniversary%20celebration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20young%20musician%20who%20once%20sang%20to%20strangers%20on%20the%20street%2C%20being%20invited%20to%20Deshaj%20is%20both%20a%20milestone%20and%20a%20powerful%20affirmation%20of%20his%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonali%20Chakraborty%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F470547%2Fmoram-birbhum-tribal-women-empowerment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eco-founder%20of%20Moram%20Earth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shares%20her%20thoughts%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20day%20of%20the%208th%20anniversary%20of%20Deshaj%20store%20and%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20we%20proudly%20continue%20our%20journey%20of%20nurturing%20dreams%20and%20giving%20voice%20to%20the%20unheard.%20This%20celebration%20is%20not%20just%20a%20milestone%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20movement.%20Honouring%20the%20talent%20of%20young%20artists%20like%20Debraj%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20who%20we%20are.%20Deshaj%20has%20always%20been%20committed%20to%20uplifting%20disadvantaged%20young%2C%20talented%20artists%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20giving%20them%20the%20platform%2C%20voice%2C%20and%20visibility%20they%20truly%20deserve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-ca