ta-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475020%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESushmita%E2%80%99s%20workshops%20teach%20how%201%20kg%20of%20water%20hyacinth%20can%20be%20turned%20into%2030%20sheets%20of%20paper.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20University%20of%20Hamburg%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20a%20wood%20chemistry%20lab%20with%20Professor%20Bodosake%2C%20who%20specialises%20in%20pulp-making%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20we%20began%20experimenting%20with%20water%20hyacinth%20as%20a%20paper%20raw%20material.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20surprised%20even%20the%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNormally%2C%20making%20paper%20from%20wood%20pulp%20uses%20around%2060%25%20soda.%20But%20we%20found%20that%20with%20water%20hyacinth%2C%20you%20only%20need%20about%206%25.%20And%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20pulp%20was%20excellent%20%E2%80%94%20strong%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20work%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20proved%20what%20she%20had%20long%20suspected%20%E2%80%94%20water%20hyacinth%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20a%20burden.%20With%20the%20right%20technique%2C%20it%20could%20become%20a%20sustainable%2C%20scalable%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBack%20home%2C%20but%20not%20yet%20on%20board%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergised%20by%20her%20success%20in%20Germany%2C%20Sushmita%20returned%20to%20India%20with%20a%20clear%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20to%20scale%2